07:29.225 --> 07:33.396
It tapped on my desk.
It sat in my lap.

07:34.522 --> 07:35.982
- It's like...
- Sorry.

07:36.024 --> 07:38.318
It's like a...

07:38.401 --> 07:40.070
It's like a sidekick.

07:40.153 --> 07:43.323
My little ugly sidekick.
It was very odd.

08:01.424 --> 08:03.510
Eww.

08:03.593 --> 08:05.762
- Oh, oh!
- What?

08:05.845 --> 08:08.431
- Oh!
- What?!

08:08.515 --> 08:10.016
How about this?

08:10.100 --> 08:14.145
A spray can, see?
And you spray it on dog poo...

08:14.187 --> 08:17.023
and the poo disappears.

08:17.107 --> 08:18.983
- Disappears?
- Yes!

08:19.025 --> 08:21.027
Where does it go?

08:21.069 --> 08:23.071
Who knows? But the thing is...

08:23.154 --> 08:26.157
