19:20.728 --> 19:23.523
- Tomorrow we'll have pancakes.
- Fine.

19:28.820 --> 19:30.822
I don't want any more cereal.

19:30.864 --> 19:33.950
Eat up, otherwise you don't
get to play with Corky, okay?

19:39.789 --> 19:41.499
- What?
- Nothing.

19:42.333 --> 19:44.210
Why are you always asking "what"?

19:44.252 --> 19:46.588
- I'm not always asking "what."
- Yes, you are.

19:46.671 --> 19:48.214
It's true, Dad, you are.

19:48.298 --> 19:50.759
Well, because I know there's something.

19:50.842 --> 19:55.263
- And you know exactly what it is.
- Then why do you always say "nothing"?

19:55.346 --> 19:57.724
- Corky!
- Hold Lula's hand, honey.

20:00.935 --> 20:03.229
- Corky!

20:03.354 --> 20:04.898
So beautiful.

20:04.981 --> 20:07.400
Such a great horse, Corky.

20:07.442 --> 20:09.527
Who's a good boy?

20:09.611 --> 20:13.698
Corky's a sweet and gentle horse
and me and the kids love him.

20:13.782 --> 20:16.868
Corky happens to shit
the size of a breadbasket

20:16.910 --> 20:19.954
in our yard every day
when he comes to visit.

21:00.370 --> 21:02.455
What are you doing?

21:02.539 --> 21:05.125
Nothing. Nothing at all.

21:05.208 --> 21:11.005
I'm just throwing away some more
completely useless inventions.

21:12.715 --> 21:15.593
For chrissakes, Debbie, light?
Light?! Come on!

21:15.635 --> 21:17.971
Come on! This was shit.

21:18.012 --> 21:21.975
You think Edison would've looked up
from his workbench at some shit spray?

21:22.016 --> 21:23.977
Yes. Yes, I do.

21:24.018 --> 21:27.439
Because, you see, a good invention
is a good invention!

21:27.480 --> 21:30.358
I got news for you, sister.
Edison ain't looking up.

21:30.442 --> 21:33.778
Sister. Sister?!

21:33.820 --> 21:35.196
I'm calling you sister.

21:35.280 --> 21:37.866
You should be so lucky
to be my sister.

21:37.949 --> 21:39.784
She knows what she's talking about.

21:39.826 --> 21:41.661
Windtalker, or whatever her name is.

21:41.745 --> 21:46.249
- Do not call her that. It's Windsong.
- Windsong. My mistake. Windsong.

21:46.332 --> 21:46.750
Knockety, knockety.
A-knock, knock, knock.

21:46.750 --> 21:49.169
Knockety, knockety.
A-knock, knock, knock.

21:49.252 --> 21:52.297
How's everybody doing?

21:56.718 --> 21:58.470
What a day, right?

21:58.511 --> 22:01.306
My God! Can you believe
the coffee that makes?

22:01.347 --> 22:04.100
I knew you'd love it.
Let's go, tiger.

22:07.645 --> 22:10.857
Look who's here, will you please?

22:11.566 --> 22:13.818
Look who's here. It's okay, poopie.

22:13.860 --> 22:16.988
Have you been stealing apples again,
you little rascal?

22:17.072 --> 22:20.492
