has Corky become a nuisance?

22:20.533 --> 22:21.868
- No.
- Not one bit.

22:21.951 --> 22:24.162
Natalie says, "Keep the corral closed."

22:24.204 --> 22:27.540
But Corky's so crazy about your apples,
I don't know what to do.

22:27.624 --> 22:29.959
No more apples for you.
No more apples...

22:30.043 --> 22:34.005
I can't stop him. He loves your apples.
Are you sure he's not a problem?

22:34.047 --> 22:36.382
- Positive.
- You guys are so fantastic.

22:36.424 --> 22:39.302
Well, my buddy boy,
let's go shoot us some golf.

22:39.302 --> 22:39.719
Well, my buddy boy,
let's go shoot us some golf.

22:55.443 --> 22:57.821
I got something for you.
I'll be right back.

22:57.904 --> 23:00.490
- Nick, no. Please.
- Yes. You'll love it.

23:00.573 --> 23:02.909
You don't have to get me anything else.

23:10.959 --> 23:12.377
When I hit it big,

23:12.419 --> 23:16.005
everyone said I should buy a house
in Beverly Hills, Bel Air or Malibu.

23:16.089 --> 23:18.883
"Why you spending money
on a mansion in the Valley?"

23:18.925 --> 23:23.054
But I love my neighborhood, and being
across the street from my best friend.

23:23.138 --> 23:26.099
Do you see how it moves in the wind?
That's what I love.

23:27.767 --> 23:31.396
It flaps different than cheaper fabric.
Do you notice that?

23:32.564 --> 23:34.774
- Yeah.
- And it makes you feel better.

23:34.858 --> 23:39.738
Nice fabric makes you feel better!
It's mind-blowing, isn't it?

23:39.779 --> 23:42.115
Nick, you buy us too much.

23:42.198 --> 23:46.619
Too much?! You're my best friend.
Nice things make life nicer.

23:48.538 --> 23:51.958
All right, let's take another look
at that follow-through.

23:53.460 --> 23:55.920
I want the head down.

23:59.257 --> 24:00.633
That is nice, Nicky.

24:00.717 --> 24:02.761
- Right?
- Very nice.

24:02.802 --> 24:05.513
God Almighty, Mr. Dingman.

24:05.597 --> 24:08.266
Nick? Can I talk to you for a second?

24:10.977 --> 24:12.520
Just take a second.

24:14.647 --> 24:17.150
Can't it just be us?
You and me playing golf?

24:17.233 --> 24:19.277
