It means nothing to me.

24:22.113 --> 24:23.364
Let's just enjoy it.

24:25.200 --> 24:27.118
Why can't you come with us?

24:27.160 --> 24:28.995
Because Daddy has to go to work.

24:29.079 --> 24:31.498
You'll have a great time
at Aunt Nancy's.

24:31.581 --> 24:34.459
Aunt Windsong, and you know that.

24:35.293 --> 24:37.378
