24:42.300 --> 24:46.137
Honey, you don't have to do this.
Really. Why do this?

24:46.179 --> 24:50.100
Because I have to do this.
We have to do this.

24:50.183 --> 24:52.143
Something has to change.

24:52.185 --> 24:55.188
I can't look at you,
I can't look across the street.

24:55.271 --> 24:57.524
